OL,3,CResident doctors in England vote to
OL,4,Cstrike over pay offer
OL,6,FResident doctors, formerly known as
OL,7,Fjunior doctors, in England have voted
OL,8,Fto go on strike over what they
OL,9,Fdescribe as a pay offer that makes "no
OL,10,Fmeaningful progress" towards fair and
OL,11,Fattractive remuneration.
OL,13,FThe decision to take industrial action
OL,14,Fwas passed, with 90% of those who took
OL,15,Fpart voting to proceed with strikes.
OL,17,FThe walk-outs could last until January
OL,18,Fof next year, the British Medical
OL,19,FAssociation (BMA) has announced.
