OL,3,CResident doctors in England vote to
OL,4,Cstrike over pay offer
OL,6,FIt comes after the government's pay
OL,7,Freview body announced its
OL,8,Frecommendation of a 4% pay increase
OL,9,Fplus a one-time payment of #750 in
OL,10,F2025/6 for all resident doctors.
OL,12,FAlthough the BMA said this somewhat
OL,13,Fmitigates the effects of rising costs,
OL,14,Fit stressed that when you take into
OL,15,Faccount inflation, this offer is
OL,16,Frendered meaningless and makes too
OL,17,Flittle progress towards their ultimate
OL,18,Fgoal of full pay restoration.
OL,20,FThe ballot opened on May 27 and closed
OL,21,Fon Monday.
