OL,4,Cstrike over pay offer
OL,6,FAll BMA resident doctor members
OL,7,Femployed by NHS organisations were
OL,8,Feligible to vote.
OL,10,FTrade union ballots require a turnout
OL,11,Fof 50% of eligible voters to be
OL,12,Fconsidered to have support for
OL,13,Findustrial action.
OL,15,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,16,FCare said that the Health Secretary
OL,17,FWes Streeting would be meeting with
OL,18,Fthe BMA co-chairs on Monday afternoon.
