OL,6,F"The Secretary of State has been clear
OL,7,Fthat he wants to work constructively
OL,8,Fwith all unions, including the BMA, to
OL,9,Fimprove working conditions for NHS
OL,10,Fstaff and avoid strike action, which
OL,11,Fcan be hugely disruptive for patients."
OL,13,FSpeaking after announcing the ballot,
OL,14,Fresident doctor co-chairs, Dr Melissa
OL,15,FRyan and Dr Ross Nieuwoudt said: "Last
OL,16,Fweek the government finally told us
OL,17,Fwhat it would do to restore the pay of
OL,18,Fdoctors: almost nothing. Doctors have
OL,19,Fseen their pay decline by 23% in real
OL,20,Fterms since 2008.
