OL,3,CResident doctors in England vote to
OL,4,Cstrike over pay offer
OL,6,FResident doctors in England have been
OL,7,Fdemanding what they call "full pay
OL,8,Frestoration." They claim that the
OL,9,Faccumulated effects of below-inflation
OL,10,Fpay rises have combined since 2008 to
OL,11,Ferode their real-terms pay by around a
OL,12,Ffifth.
OL,14,FResident doctors had previously said a
OL,15,F5% pay offer would be the minimum
OL,16,Famount they would consider accepting.
OL,17,FThey have instead been offered a 4%
OL,18,Frise and a one-off payment of #750 for
OL,19,Fthe year 2025/6.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
